OL,3,CFamily of Brit couple killed in Spain
OL,4,Cwildfires 'heartbroken'
OL,6,FThe family of a British couple killed
OL,7,Fin wildfires in Spain have spoken of
OL,8,Ftheir heartbreak.
OL,10,FPete and Fran Gillam, who lived in the
OL,11,Fvillage of Bedar, were among at least
OL,12,F13 people, including a number of
OL,13,FBritons, who lost their lives in
OL,14,FSpain's Almeria province following
OL,15,Ffires which broke out last Thursday.
OL,26,@sD@Mrr
