CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1784053122
OL,3,CFamily of Brit couple killed in Spain
OL,4,Cwildfires 'heartbroken'
OL,6,FTheir daughter Danielle Gillam-Kirton,
OL,7,Ffrom Sheffield, posted the news on
OL,8,Fsocial media. She said: "We are
OL,9,Fheartbroken to share that we have
OL,10,Freceived confirmation from the police
OL,11,Fthat mum and sad did not survive the
OL,12,Ffire.
OL,14,F"Thank you for all your love, support
OL,15,Fand prayers over the past few days.
OL,16,FThey have meant more to us than we can
OL,17,Fever express."
OL,19,FThe family had been searching for the
OL,20,Fcouple for several days and had
OL,21,Fappealed for help to find them.
OL,26,@yD@NO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
