PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1784053122
OL,3,CFamily of Brit couple killed in Spain
OL,4,Cwildfires 'heartbroken'
OL,6,FBut attempts to contact them were
OL,7,Funsuccessful.
OL,9,FA post on the community Facebook
OL,10,Fgroup, Bedar Village People, said:
OL,11,F"With deepest regret we can now
OL,12,Fconfirm Fran and Pete Gillam lost
OL,13,Ftheir lives in the fire."
OL,15,FIt is believed the fire started in Los
OL,16,FGallardos amid temperatures often
OL,17,Fexceeding 40C, before spreading across
OL,18,Fabout 7,000 hectares of land.
OL,26,@rD@Irr
