OL,3,CFamily of Brit couple killed in Spain
OL,4,Cwildfires 'heartbroken'
OL,6,FSpain has experienced several days of
OL,7,Frecord-setting heat, with more than
OL,8,F1,000 excess deaths.
OL,10,FA Foreign Office spokesman said: "Our
OL,11,Fthoughts are with all those impacted
OL,12,Fby the devastating wildfires in Spain."
OL,14,F"We are supporting British nationals
OL,15,Faffected and their families and remain
OL,16,Fin close contact with the Spanish
OL,17,Fauthorities."
OL,26,@rD@bOUvD@AOUyD@MO]
